    <text type="letter">
        <body>
 
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place">431 Stevens Street</name>
                    <name type="place">Camden New Jersey</name>
                    <date when="1884-01-10" rend="right">Jan: 10 '84</date>
                </dateline>
                <salute>Dear Sir</salute>
            </opener>
            <p>Yes, I have <choice><abbr>rec'd</abbr><expan>received</expan></choice> the Dresden pamphlet<ptr
                    target="uva.00476_n2"/>&#8212;I enclose you a late article of mine from the <hi
                    rend="italic">Critic</hi><ptr target="uva.00476_n3"/>&#8212;I keep about as
                usual in health this winter&#8212;How do you get on with your new book?</p>
            <closer>
                <signed>Walt Whitman</signed>
            </closer>

        </body>
